Yehia Dessouki (Arabic: يحيى دسوقى; amụrụ na 13 Machị 1978) bụ onye Ijipt na-ese ihe na onye na-ese foto
Ọ na-eme nka nke oge a site na iji ụdị mgbasa ozi dị iche iche ma ọdịnala ma dijitalụ
Ọ bụkwa onye na-ese ụkpụrụ ụlọ, onye gụsịrị akwụkwọ na ngalaba nke nka mara mma, ngalaba ihe owuwu, nke Mahadum Helwan

O sonyere n'ọtụtụ ihe ngosi otu na-egosi ọtụtụ ọrụ nka na-egosi isiokwu dị iche iche, dị ka: Architecture of Old Islamic Cairo - Still Life - Lanterns of Ramadan Fawanees - Circus, ma mesịa mee ihe ngosi mbụ ya banyere "Joy of Roses" gụnyere ihe osise pastel dị nro yana ihe osise mmanụ.
Yehia Dessouki nwere ụdị pụrụ iche, nke dị ịrịba ama maka ojiji ọ na-eji ihe osise mara mma ọtụtụ n'ime ọrụ nka ya.
Ịzụlite ya n'etiti ezinụlọ na-ese ihe bụ mmetụta dị mkpa na ndụ nka ya
Nna ya bụ onye na-ese ihe Batik Ali Dessouki ebe nne ya bụ onye nkatọ nka na onye ọka iwu

Mmetụta ndị ọzọ bịara dika o mere njem ọmụmụ oge okpomọkụ ya na Ịtali (Società Dante Alighieri), na-enye ya ohere ọlaedo ileta ebe ngosi nka na Rom, Milan, Florence na Pisa na nke kachasị mkpa, ileta Venice Biennial of Plastic Arts.

N'ihi mmasị ya maka ihe osise dijitalụ, o mere ụfọdụ ọrụ nka dijitalụ dị iche iche nke nnwale karịsịa na eserese dijitalụ na-egosi isiokwu nka ọhụrụ nke a na-agwakọta n'etiti Marionettes nke ihe nkiri na calligraphy Arabic
Otu n'ime ihe osise dijitalụ ndị ahụ bụ ọrụ nka dijitalụ mbụ e bipụtara n'ihu akwụkwọ akụkọ Egypt bụ Akhbar Al-Adab, nke bụ akwụkwọ akụkọ Egypt a ma ama nke ndị isi ọdịbendị Egypt na-agụ.
Igbe na iko ndị nwụrụ anwụ
